## 4. API Endpoints

| Method | Path | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| GET | `/api/launches` | Launches with status |
| GET | `/api/launches/report` | Full daily report |
| GET | `/api/launches/trends` | 30-day pass rate trend |
| GET | `/api/test-items/launch/:id` | Test items for a launch |
| GET | `/api/test-items/untriaged` | Untriaged failed items |
| GET | `/api/test-items/:id/logs` | Logs for a test item |
| POST | `/api/triage/:itemId` | Classify defect type (Zod validated) |
| POST | `/api/triage/:itemId/comment` | Add comment (Zod validated) |
| POST | `/api/triage/bulk` | Bulk triage (Zod validated) |
| POST | `/api/analysis/:launchId/:type` | Trigger RP analysis |
| POST | `/api/jira/create` | Create Jira bug |
| POST | `/api/jira/link` | Link Jira issue |
| GET | `/api/jira/search` | Search Jira |
| GET | `/api/acknowledgment/today` | Today's ack status |
| POST | `/api/acknowledgment` | Acknowledge report (Zod validated) |
| GET | `/api/flaky-tests` | Top flaky tests |
| GET | `/api/defect-types` | Available defect types |
| GET | `/api/activity` | Activity feed |
| GET | `/api/config` | Public configuration |
| GET | `/health` | Health check |

