## 5. Client Pages

| Route | Page | Purpose |
|-------|------|---------|
| `/` | DashboardPage | Status matrix, health overview, acknowledgment |
| `/launch/:launchId` | LaunchDetailPage | Test items, logs, triage, similar failures |
| `/failures` | FailuresPage | Untriaged and failed items across launches |
| `/trends` | TrendsPage | 30-day pass rate charts |
| `/flaky` | FlakyTestsPage | Tests that flip between pass and fail |
| `/activity` | ActivityPage | Triage and acknowledgment activity feed |
| `/settings` | SettingsPage | Configuration and preferences |

