## 6. Configuration

All configuration via environment variables (see `packages/server/src/config.ts`):

| Variable | Purpose | Default |
|----------|---------|---------|
| `REPORTPORTAL_URL` | RP API base URL | (internal Red Hat URL) |
| `REPORTPORTAL_TOKEN` | RP auth token | (required) |
| `REPORTPORTAL_PROJECT` | RP project name | CNV |
| `SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL` | Slack incoming webhook | (disabled if empty) |
| `SMTP_HOST`, `SMTP_PORT`, etc. | Email config | (disabled if empty) |
| `JIRA_URL`, `JIRA_TOKEN` | Jira config | (disabled if empty) |
| `CRON_SCHEDULE` | Poll schedule | `0 7 * * *` |
| `DASHBOARD_PORT` | Server port | 8080 |
| `DB_PATH` | SQLite file location | `./data/monitor.db` |

