## 7. Data Flow

```
K8s CronJob (7 AM) в†’ pollReportPortal() в†’ ReportPortal API
                         в†“
                   SQLite (launches, test_items)
                         в†“
                   buildDailyReport() в†’ Slack + Email

K8s Deployment в†’ Express в†’ serves React SPA + REST API
                   в†“
         React (TanStack Query) в†’ /api/* в†’ SQLite + RP + Jira
```

