## 8. Development

```bash
npm install                   # Install all workspaces
npm run dev                   # Concurrently: server (8080) + client (5173 with proxy)
npm run dev:server            # Server only
npm run dev:client            # Client only (Vite)
npm run build                 # Build shared в†’ server в†’ client
npm run typecheck             # TypeScript check (shared + server)
npm run test                  # Vitest (server)
npm run lint                  # ESLint (0 errors, 0 warnings enforced)
npm run lint:fix              # ESLint autofix
npm run format                # Prettier format all files
npm run format:check          # Prettier check (CI)
npm run knip                  # Unused code/dependency detection
npm run poll                  # Run one poll cycle
```

