## 9. Code Quality Toolchain

- **ESLint 9** flat config with 14 plugins (typescript-eslint, react, sonarjs, unicorn, jsx-a11y, promise, security, regexp, boundaries, perfectionist, prettier, simple-import-sort, react-refresh, tanstack-query)
- **Prettier** for formatting (single quotes, trailing commas, 100 char width)
- **Knip** for unused code/dependency detection
- **Husky + lint-staged** pre-commit hooks (ESLint autofix + Prettier on staged files, format:check, Knip)
- **CI**: lint (--max-warnings 0), format:check, knip, typecheck, test, build

